Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.10,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.51,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,你一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.95,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,既沒有事物待守
