Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.86,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,沒有欲求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
